Known source-asset coverage gaps
--------------------------------

The authoritative coverage-gap records are in SOURCE-MEMBER-POLICY.json and
are copied into WIRELESS-FIRMWARE-PROVENANCE.json. They include ATH11K,
MT7603/MT7628, BCM203x/BFUSB, Broadcom HCD and Intel Bluetooth firmware absent
from the pinned source asset. Their driver symbols must not be treated as
hardware-tested merely because a module was produced.
